      Open the game Console:
      Hit the key " ` " or " ~ " also known as Tilde.
      A CONSOLE window should open with a cursor.
      Enter your codes.
      Hit " ` " or " ~ " to leave the console.
   b) Use the Debug or Cheat Hot Keys as shown in the "Define Keys" area 
      as explained above.


